### FoodOptionType API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5132/api/foodoptiontype

### Get all food option types
GET {{baseUrl}}

### Get a specific food option type by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/1

### Get food option types by entree
GET {{baseUrl}}/entree/1

### Get food option types with options by entree
GET {{baseUrl}}/with-options/entree/1

### Create a new food option type
POST {{baseUrl}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 0,
  "name": "Toppings",
  "description": "Choose your toppings",
  "isMandatory": false,
  "maxSelections": 3
}

### Update a food option type
PUT {{baseUrl}}/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "Toppings",
  "description": "Choose your favorite toppings",
  "isMandatory": true,
  "maxSelections": 5
}

### Delete a food option type
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/1
